data.description: What a lovely 3 bedroom, 2 1/2 bathroom that sits in a great and cul-de-sac.  This home has a spacious deck, fenced secluded backyard with lots of room and a shed included. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances that are included along with the washer and dryer.  Large loft area and bathrooms have updates as well. This wonderful home has a nice size living room and dining room combo that is great for entertaining family and friends, 2 car garage with keyless entry. Furnace and AC unit is 2 years old and the water heater is 3 years old. Close to shopping, banking, library, eateries and the highway.  Don't miss this opportunity so schedule a showing today.
